# UDS Design System

You are building UI with the **Urban Design System (UDS)**.

**CRITICAL — 3 rules you must NEVER violate:**
1. **NEVER use `--uds-primitive-*` tokens.** Only use semantic tokens (`--uds-color-*`, `--uds-space-*`, `--uds-font-*`). Primitives don't change with themes.
2. **NEVER hardcode colors, spacing, or fonts.** No `#171717`, no `16px`, no `'Inter'`. Always `var(--uds-*)`.
3. **NEVER load `uds.js` in React or Vue.** React uses hooks. Vue uses refs. Only vanilla HTML uses uds.js.

**Docs:** https://sbajwa32.github.io/uds-docs/
**AI context (JSON):** https://sbajwa32.github.io/uds-docs/ai-context.json
**Install:** `npm install uds-core` then `import 'uds-core/uds.css'`
**Icons:** Material Symbols Outlined — browse at https://fonts.google.com/icons

## Naming Convention

All UDS component classes use the **`udc-`** prefix (Urban Design Component). Naming follows BEM:
- Block: `udc-{component}` (e.g. `udc-dropdown`)
- Element: `udc-{component}__{part}` (e.g. `udc-dropdown__trigger`)
- Variants via data attributes: `data-variant`, `data-size`, `data-state`

**NEVER** invent classes with `uds-`, `udc_`, or unprefixed names. If UDS doesn't have a component for it, build custom CSS using UDS tokens.

## Common UI Pattern → UDS Component

| If you need... | Use this UDS component |
|----------------|----------------------|
| Toast / alert / banner | `udc-notification` |
| Modal / popup / confirm | `udc-dialog` |
| Select / dropdown menu | `udc-dropdown` |
| Tag / filter pill | `udc-chip` |
| Status label / indicator | `udc-badge` |
| Card with action / selection | `udc-tile` |
| Sidebar navigation | `udc-nav-vertical` |
| Top application bar | `udc-nav-header` |
| Search bar with clear | `udc-search` |
| Data grid / table | `udc-data-table` |
| Hover info popup | `udc-tooltip` |
| Toggle / switch | NOT in UDS — build custom with tokens |
| Pagination | NOT in UDS — build custom with tokens |
| Accordion | NOT in UDS — build custom with tokens |

## Framework Detection

Check `package.json`:
- `react` in dependencies → React (className, hooks, NO uds.js)
- `vue` in dependencies → Vue (class, ref, script setup, NO uds.js)
- Otherwise → vanilla HTML (class, uds.js handles behavior)

## Required External Links

ALWAYS include in `<head>`:
```html
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;700&family=Poppins:wght@400;500;700&family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&family=Lexend:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" rel="stylesheet" />
```

## Token Architecture — Primitives vs Semantics

**PRIMITIVE tokens** (`--uds-primitive-*`): Raw values. NEVER change. **NEVER use in code.**
**SEMANTIC tokens** (`--uds-color-*`, `--uds-space-*`, `--uds-font-*`): Purpose-based. Change with themes. **ALWAYS use.**

Flow: `Figma → Primitive → Semantic → Your code`

## Theming

Set data attributes on `<html>`. Semantic tokens change automatically. Your code stays the same.

```
--uds-color-surface-main: #fafafa  (light)  →  #1a1a1a  (dark)
--uds-color-text-interactive: #005ff0 (base) →  #0066cc  (resman brand)
```

| Attribute | Values | Default |
|-----------|--------|---------|
| `data-color-scheme` | `dark` | light |
| `data-theme` | `resman`, `anyonehome`, `inhabit` | base |
| `data-font` | `poppins`, `roboto`, `lexend` | Inter |
| `data-font-scale` | `smaller`, `larger` | default |
| `data-density` | `comfortable` | compact |

Dark mode: `<html data-color-scheme="dark">` — everything adapts.

## Tokens — When to Use Which

### Surfaces
| Token | Use for |
|-------|---------|
| `--uds-color-surface-page-main` | Page background |
| `--uds-color-surface-main` | Cards, content areas |
| `--uds-color-surface-subtle` | Headers, table headers |
| `--uds-color-surface-alt` | Zebra stripes, code blocks |
| `--uds-color-surface-interactive-default` | Primary button fill |
| `--uds-color-surface-info-subtle` / `success-subtle` / `warning-subtle` / `error-subtle` | Status containers |

### Text
| Token | Use for |
|-------|---------|
| `--uds-color-text-primary` | Body text, headings |
| `--uds-color-text-secondary` | Helper text, labels, captions |
| `--uds-color-text-inverse` | Text on filled backgrounds |
| `--uds-color-text-interactive` | Links, active items |
| `--uds-color-text-disabled` | Disabled fields |

### Spacing
`--uds-space-050` (4px), `--uds-space-100` (8px), `--uds-space-150` (12px), `--uds-space-200` (16px), `--uds-space-300` (24px), `--uds-space-400` (32px), `--uds-space-500` (40px), `--uds-space-600` (48px), `--uds-space-700` (56px), `--uds-space-1000` (80px)

### Typography
- Family: `var(--uds-font-family)` — NEVER hardcode
- Size: `--uds-font-size-xs` (10), `sm` (12), `base` (14), `md` (16), `lg` (18), `xl` (20), `2xl` (24), `3xl` (28), `5xl` (36)
- Weight: `--uds-font-weight-regular` (400), `medium` (500), `bold` (700)

### Text Style Classes (optional)
`.uds-text-heading-xl`, `.uds-text-heading-lg`, `.uds-text-paragraph-base`, `.uds-text-label-base-bold`, `.uds-text-label-sm-medium`

### Border Radius
`--uds-border-radius-container-sm` (4px), `--uds-border-radius-input` (8px), `--uds-border-radius-container-md` (12px), `--uds-border-radius-container-xl` (24px), `--uds-border-radius-container-full` (9999px)

### Shadows
`--uds-shadow-depth-100` (hover), `--uds-shadow-depth-300` (dropdown), `--uds-shadow-depth-500` (dialog), `--uds-overlay-backdrop` (dialog overlay)

## Icons

Use **Material Symbols Outlined**. Browse: https://fonts.google.com/icons

Use `udc-icon-wrapper` for standalone icons that need standardized sizing (16/20/24/32/48px):
```html
<span class="udc-icon-wrapper" data-size="24"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">info</span></span>
```
Use bare `<span class="material-symbols-outlined">` inside UDS components that already handle icon sizing (buttons, nav, notification, etc.).

**Common icons:**
- Navigation: `space_dashboard`, `book`, `contact_phone`, `home_work`, `monetization_on`, `settings`, `account_circle`, `notifications`
- Actions: `add`, `edit`, `delete`, `close`, `search`, `clear`, `download`, `more_vert`, `chevron_right`, `keyboard_arrow_down`
- Status: `info`, `check_circle`, `error_outline`, `warning_amber`

## Components — 21 Available

### Button
`udc-button-primary` / `udc-button-secondary` / `udc-button-ghost`
Variants: `data-size="sm"`, `data-leading-icon`, `data-trailing-icon`, `data-icon-only`, `data-btn-color="danger"`, `disabled`
```html
<button class="udc-button-primary">Save</button>
<button class="udc-button-secondary">Cancel</button>
<button class="udc-button-ghost" data-icon-only>
  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">more_vert</span>
</button>
```

### Text Input
`udc-text-input` → `__label`, `__required`, `__field`, `__helper`, `__counter`, `__trailing-btn`
States: `data-state="error"`
```html
<div class="udc-text-input">
  <label class="udc-text-input__label">Email<span class="udc-text-input__required"></span></label>
  <div class="udc-text-input__field">
    <input type="email" placeholder="Enter email..." />
  </div>
  <div class="udc-text-input__helper">
    <span>Helper text</span>
    <span class="udc-text-input__counter">0/100</span>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Checkbox
```html
<label class="udc-checkbox">
  <input type="checkbox" />
  <span class="udc-checkbox__control"></span>
  <span class="udc-checkbox__label">Accept terms</span>
</label>
```

### Radio
```html
<div class="udc-radio-group" role="radiogroup">
  <span class="udc-radio-group__legend">Preference</span>
  <label class="udc-radio">
    <input type="radio" name="pref" value="email" />
    <span class="udc-radio__control"></span>
    <span class="udc-radio__label">Email</span>
  </label>
</div>
```

### Dropdown
`udc-dropdown` → `__label`, `__trigger`, `__value`, `__chevron`, `__list`, `__item`, `__helper`
States: `data-open="true"`, `data-state="error"`, `aria-disabled="true"`
```html
<div class="udc-dropdown">
  <label class="udc-dropdown__label">Property</label>
  <div class="udc-dropdown__trigger" tabindex="0" role="combobox" aria-expanded="false">
    <span class="udc-dropdown__value" data-placeholder>Select...</span>
    <span class="udc-dropdown__chevron">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">keyboard_arrow_down</span>
    </span>
  </div>
  <div class="udc-dropdown__list" role="listbox">
    <div class="udc-dropdown__item" role="option">Option A</div>
    <div class="udc-dropdown__item" role="option">Option B</div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Search
`udc-search` → `__field`, `__icon`, `__clear`
States: `data-state="error"`, `data-has-value="true"`
```html
<div class="udc-search">
  <div class="udc-search__field">
    <span class="udc-search__icon">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">search</span>
    </span>
    <input type="search" placeholder="Search..." />
    <button class="udc-search__clear" aria-label="Clear">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">clear</span>
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Badge
```html
<span class="udc-badge" data-variant="success">Active</span>
<span class="udc-badge" data-variant="warning">Pending</span>
<span class="udc-badge" data-variant="error">Overdue</span>
